  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel offers a traditional Portuguese continental breakfast each day in the <strong>Botânico</strong> restaurant</p>
<p>The restaurant is also open in the evenings. The traditional Portuguese menu uses a lot of locally-farmed produce and offers an excellent example of Madeiran cuisine.</p>
<p>During the day there are light snacks and drinks available at the pool bar, and in the evenings the lobby bar is a great place to enjoy a quiet drink.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
