  <description><![CDATA[<p>Located in the centre of Funchal’s Lido area, this four-star hotel is just a short walk from the beach, the Praia Formosa and the natural sea pools at the Balnear Lido. It's also within easy reach of the city centre where you can wander the cobbled streets, explore the markets and the famous <a data-udi="umb://document/b99bc93beefb425a905ffd631cf6d85b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b99bc93beefb425a905ffd631cf6d85b}" title="Madeira" data-anchor="#">Madeira</a> wine cellars, or catch the gondola to the botanical gardens.</p>
<h2>Contemporary design and stunning sea views</h2>
<p>The hotel offers contemporary interiors, careful design, and an outdoor swimming pool with a terrace that's perfect for enjoying the stunning ocean views.</p>
<p>The rooms are bright, spacious, and equipped with everything you need for a comfortable stay. Each has a balcony with panoramic views of the Atlantic Ocean or the city of Funchal.</p>
<h2>A restaurant offering traditional food, locally grown</h2>
<p>There are many restaurants and bars to explore nearby, but the hotel's own Botânico restaurant is an excellent place to sample local cuisine. Working in partnership with local farmers, they serve traditional and delicious Portuguese dishes, bringing a taste of Madeira to the table. The pool bar offers a selection of snacks and drinks throughout the day, and in the evenings can enjoy a relaxing aperitif at the lobby bar.</p>
<p><strong>Transfer time:</strong> Approx 25 minutes from Madeira Airport.</p>]]></description>
