  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Twin</strong> sleep two, with space for a cot if required. The rooms have views over the city, and are also available for sole occupancy (supplement applies).</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Twin  Partial Ocean View</strong> sleep two, with space for a cot if required. These rooms are also available for sole occupancy (supplement applies).</p>
<p><strong>Ocean View Twin</strong> sleep two, with space for a cot if required. These rooms are also available for sole occupancy (supplement applies).</p>
<p><strong>Classic Twin, Deluxe Twin Partial Ocean View and Ocean View Twin</strong> are available for sole use, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony or terrace</li>
<li>Air conditioning</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Bath with overhead shower</li>
<li>Lounge/seating area</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available on request.</p>
<p><strong>General information</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Check-in: 2pm</li>
<li>Check-out: 12pm</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>From the 1st of June 2024 a tourist tax of approx. €2.00 per person per night, for a maximum of 7 nights is payable locally for guests age 13 years and over (subject to change).</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
